---
---

<section class="section" id="portafolio">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="badge">Experiencia & Capacidades</span>
      <h2>Tecnología que Impulsa su Negocio</h2>
      <p>Combinamos desarrollo de software, automatización e infraestructura para ofrecer soluciones integrales.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      <!-- Desarrollo Web Full Stack -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Desarrollo Web Full Stack</h3>
        <p>Aplicaciones robustas con Laravel, Next.js y arquitecturas modernas escalables.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">Laravel</span>
          <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
          <span class="tag">REST APIs</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Automatización de Procesos -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automatización de Procesos</h3>
        <p>Eliminamos tareas repetitivas con scripts personalizados e integraciones entre plataformas.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">Scripts</span>
          <span class="tag">Integraciones</span>
          <span class="tag">Workflows</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Seguridad & Auditoría -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seguridad & Auditoría</h3>
        <p>Análisis de vulnerabilidades, hardening de sistemas y configuración de protocolos de seguridad.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">Pentesting</span>
          <span class="tag">Firewall</span>
          <span class="tag">SSL/TLS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sistemas de Gestión -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sistemas de Gestión</h3>
        <p>ERP, CRM y dashboards personalizados para el control total de la operación empresarial.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">ERP</span>
          <span class="tag">CRM</span>
          <span class="tag">Dashboards</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Infraestructura Cloud -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Infraestructura Cloud</h3>
        <p>Despliegue, migración y optimización de infraestructura en entornos cloud profesionales.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">AWS</span>
          <span class="tag">VPS</span>
          <span class="tag">CI/CD</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Soporte Técnico Remoto -->
      <div class="portfolio-card card">
        <div class="portfolio-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Soporte Técnico Remoto</h3>
        <p>Diagnóstico, resolución de incidencias y mantenimiento preventivo sin desplazamientos físicos.</p>
        <div class="portfolio-tags">
          <span class="tag">Remoto</span>
          <span class="tag">24/7</span>
          <span class="tag">Monitoreo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #portafolio {
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
  }

  .portfolio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .portfolio-card {
    padding: 36px 28px;
  }

  .portfolio-icon {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(74, 127, 167, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74, 127, 167, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .portfolio-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .portfolio-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .portfolio-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    background: rgba(74, 127, 167, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74, 127, 167, 0.18);
    border-radius: 50px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .portfolio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .portfolio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
